<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Page Not Found - Wedding Site</title>
  <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .error-page {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .error-page h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #e91e63;
    }
    .error-page p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #6c757d;
    }
    .error-page a {
      color: #e91e63;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .error-page a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .error-page img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-page">
    <!-- <img src="" alt="wedguest"> -->
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Oops! The page you are looking for is not here.</p>
    <p>It seems we can't find what you're looking for. Perhaps searching can help or <a href="/">return to the homepage</a>.</p>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
